        <updateDate>2007-07-19T21:40:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Law Enforcement Officers Safety Act of 2007 - Amends the federal criminal code to: (1) include Amtrak and executive branch police officers as qualified law enforcement officers eligible to carry concealed firearms; and (2) revise requirements for certifying retired law enforcement officers to carry concealed firearms.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
